{"title":"Copy","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-4336","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>  在那遥远的dysy有一颓废胖，他在刷oj的时候最喜欢用的算法就是 </p><p>  &lt;Ctrl+c&gt; &amp;&amp; &lt;Ctrl+v&gt;</p><p>  但是懒惰他只想用 ↑ ↓ ← →来控制光标</p><p>     现在光标在（1，1），他想知道把光标移到（n，m）最少需要多少步</p><p>于是他们请作为大犇的你来告诉他答案 =，=</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>共一行，包括两个整数：n，m</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个整数为总共的步数</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2 2</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1&lt;= n,m &lt;= 10<sup>9</sup></p><p>（一点都不大！）</p><p>                灰常简单~</p><p>                做完此题请前往4337：Copy（二）</p><p><span style=\"\">                      </span><span style=\"font-family: 'comic sans ms';\">LYL from dysy</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}